column5: Hey all,  We have an ice fishing trip planned on Nipissing starting tomorrow. Anyone have any recent reports from South bay? How much damage did the rain and warm spell do?
I came back from Nippising this Wednesday.  We have from 10"-12" of ice everythere. I don't think you need to worry.  Fishing was good.

From what I herd a lot of operators that are running bungalows canceled all reservations for this weekend. Resorts that are running day huts with cottages are still business as usual. My advice to you would be to contact your operator to make sure.  Rich.
PM'd you. Call your operator for sure.
